<h1>About Porybox</h1>

<div>

  <h2>What is Porybox?</h2>

  <p>
  Porybox is an online Pokémon viewer. It helps you organize your Pokémon collection online, see advanced information that is usually hidden in game, and share links to individual Pokémon or boxes to show off. You can also make Pokémon publicly available for download, or download Pokémon that have been made public.
  </p>
  
  <h2>Who is behind Porybox?</h2>
  
  <p>
  Porybox was created by the moderators of <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/pokemontrades/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">/r/pokemontrades<a>, a large Pokémon-trading community on reddit that focuses on legitimate, legal and uncloned Pokémon.
  </p>
  
  <h2>Supporting Porybox</h2>
  
  <p>
  Porybox is and will always remain free to use. However, running Porybox has costs associated to the domain name, the server and the bandwidth. You can help us ensure Porybox's future by donating.<br><br>
  
  <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">[ + add donation link]</a><br><br>
  
  All donations will go towards funding the server and bandwidth costs.
  </p>
  
